magicbook.gtlitecore.api.utils.stream

接口 LazyStreams.Gatherer<T,R>

  • 类型参数:
    T - The type of input elements.
    R - The type of output elements.
    封闭类:
    LazyStreams

    public static interface LazyStreams.Gatherer<T,R>
    A stateful intermediate transformation for input elements in a stream that can emit zero to more transformed elements to downstream consumers.

    This is a simplified version of Java 24 feature "Gatherer".

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 默认方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      default void begin()
      Callback invoked before element processing begins, used for initializing a transformation state.
      default void finish(java.util.function.Consumer<R> downstream)
      Callback invoked after all elements have been processed, used for finalizing transformation state and emitting any remaining elements.
      boolean gather(T element, java.util.function.Consumer<R> downstream)
      Gathers input elements and optionally emits transformed elements to downstream consumer.

    • 方法详细资料

      • gather

        boolean gather(T element,
               java.util.function.Consumer<R> downstream)
        Gathers input elements and optionally emits transformed elements to downstream consumer.
        参数:
        element - The input elements to gathered.
        downstream - The consumer for emitting result elements.
        返回:
        Returns true to continue processing, false to stop it.

      • begin

        default void begin()
        Callback invoked before element processing begins, used for initializing a transformation state.

      • finish

        default void finish(java.util.function.Consumer<R> downstream)
        Callback invoked after all elements have been processed, used for finalizing transformation state and emitting any remaining elements.
        参数:
        downstream - The consumer for emitting final result elements.
